5 department.
6 SECTION 2. LEGISLATIVE MANAGEMENT REPORT - POSTPARTUM DOULA
7 CERTIFICATION. During the 2025-26 interim, the department of health and human services
8 shall provide a report to the legislative management regarding postpartum doula certification,
9 including the status of implementing and administering the responsibilities relating to
10 postpartum doula certification under section 1 of this Act and the impact of certified doula
11 services.
